Maintainer: Will Hipson <will.hipson@hiaa.ca>
Description: Framework for creating and orchestrating data pipelines in R. Organize, 
  orchestrate, and monitor multiple pipelines in a single project. Use tags to decorate 
  functions with scheduling parameters and configuration.
